Blue Raspberry Refresher is Tea of the Week but really it’s the Tea of the YEAR ✨

This is everyone’s Favorite of the Favorites 🎉 This week it’s on our board to HONOR & REMEMBER a friend of Untamed. 
Glen Sutton III passed away as a result of a motorcycle accident right before Easter. He was a friend to every person he met. He tried everyday to make anyone around him laugh. His smile was electric. He got a Blue Raspberry Refresher everyday. This one’s for you Glenny 💥
